	* `obj == nullptr && x == 0`
* 100% pokrycia gałęzi
	* `obj != nullptr && obj->hasSomeProperty()`
	* `obj != nullptr && !obj->hasSomeProperty()`
	* `obj == nullptr && x == -11`
	* `obj == nullptr && x == 6`
